<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.7.9">
<l>kulantāṅku cātika ṇāliluṅ kīḻiḻin tettaṉai</l>
<l>nalantā ṉilātacaṇ ṭāḷacaṇ ṭāḷarka ḷākilum</l>
<l>valantāṅku cakkarat taṇṇaṉ maṇivaṇṇaṟ kāḷeṉṟuḷ</l>
<l>kalantā raṭiyār tammaṭi yārem maṭikaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those whose minds are absorbed [in the thought] “[we are] the servants</l>
<l>of the majesty with the victory-bearing discus, the one with sapphire colour”,</l>
<l>even though they be Caṇḍālas of the Caṇḍālas without any goodness</l>
<l>that are low in the four castes that uphold the families,</l>
<l>the servants of their servants [are] our lords/objects of veneration.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
